		"body": "## Summary\r\nAfter toggling an editor plugin via the eye button, pressing undo caused the mobile app to crash.\r\n\r\n## Root Cause\r\nThe [componentDidUpdate](cci:1://file:///c:/Users/LENOVO/OneDrive/Desktop/joplin/joplin/packages/app-mobile/components/screens/Note/Note.tsx:648:1-751:2) logic in [Note.tsx](cci:7://file:///c:/Users/LENOVO/OneDrive/Desktop/joplin/joplin/packages/app-mobile/components/screens/Note/Note.tsx:0:0-0:0) already resets the undo/redo state when switching `editorType` or `mode` (added in #13505). However, toggling a plugin via the eye button changes `plugins.shownEditorViewIds` — neither `editorType` nor `mode` changes. \r\n\r\nBecause the state wasn't cleared, `undoRedoButtonState.canUndo` remained `true` while the built-in editor was unmounted and `editorRef.current` became `null`. When the user tapped the undo button, it threw a null reference exception, crashing the app.\r\n\r\n## Changes\r\n1. **Extend Reset Condition:** The [componentDidUpdate](cci:1://file:///c:/Users/LENOVO/OneDrive/Desktop/joplin/joplin/packages/app-mobile/components/screens/Note/Note.tsx:648:1-751:2) reset condition has been updated to also fire when `plugins.shownEditorViewIds` changes (any plugin eye-button toggle).\r\n2. **Defense-in-Depth:** Added `?.` optional chaining to `editorRef.current?.undo()` and `editorRef.current?.redo()` as a safeguard against null-reference crashes if the button is ever visible while the editor is unmounted.\r\n\r\n### Code Diff\r\n\r\n```typescript\r\n// packages/app-mobile/components/screens/Note/Note.tsx\r\n\r\n@@ -438,7 +438,7 @@\r\n \tprivate screenHeader_undoButtonPress() {\r\n \t\tif (this.useEditorBeta()) {\r\n-\t\t\tthis.editorRef.current.undo();\r\n+\t\t\tthis.editorRef.current?.undo();\r\n \t\t} else {\r\n \t\t\tvoid this.undoRedo('undo');\r\n \t\t}\r\n\r\n@@ -445,7 +445,7 @@\r\n \tprivate screenHeader_redoButtonPress() {\r\n \t\tif (this.useEditorBeta()) {\r\n-\t\t\tthis.editorRef.current.redo();\r\n+\t\t\tthis.editorRef.current?.redo();\r\n \t\t} else {\r\n \t\t\tvoid this.undoRedo('redo');\r\n \t\t}\r\n\r\n@@ -706,7 +706,8 @@\r\n \t\t\t});\r\n \t\t}\r\n \r\n-\t\tif (this.props.visibleEditorPluginIds !== prevProps.visibleEditorPluginIds || ... ) {\r\n+\t\tconst editorPluginIdsChanged = this.props.visibleEditorPluginIds !== prevProps.visibleEditorPluginIds;\r\n+\t\tif (editorPluginIdsChanged || ... ) {\r\n \t\t\tconst { editorPlugin } = getShownPluginEditorView(this.props.plugins, this.props.windowId);\r\n \t\t\t\r\n \t\t\tif (!editorPlugin && this.props.editorNoteReloadTimeRequest > this.state.noteLastLoadTime) {\r\n \t\t\t\tvoid shared.reloadNote(this);\r\n@@ -713,4 +713,6 @@\r\n-\t\t\t\r\n-\t\t\t\t// Clear the undo / redo state ...\r\n-\t\t\t\tif (!this.useEditorBeta()) {\r\n-\t\t\t\t\tvoid this.undoRedoService_.reset();\r\n+\t\t\t}\r\n+\r\n+\t\t\tif ((!editorPlugin && ...) || editorPluginIdsChanged) {\r\n+\t\t\t\tif (!this.useEditorBeta()) {\r\n+\t\t\t\t\tvoid this.undoRedoService_.reset();\r\n",
